{"tid":1832188,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】何栢良批政府防疫落後　籲市民勿以為沙士歷史不會重現","createTime":"2020-01-21T03:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T08:26:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"67666ab5ad094d083a59af2bedf88586723b79cb","tid":1832188,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503899-20200121.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503899-20200121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6nobfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=d41be327\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503899-20200121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=739a11d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503899-20200121.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n支那武漢肺炎個案飆升，疫情蔓延至多個城市，包括與香港一河之隔的深圳。由武漢乘搭飛機抵港的旅客，凌晨起需填寫健康申報表。<br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良認為，政府應對疫情的措施落後於形勢，讓人感覺是措手不及，防疫宣傳嚴重不足，認為除了要求填寫健康申報表，政府應該採取更多防疫措施，不要等到香港出現首宗確診個案才開始行動。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良出席本台節目《千禧年代》時又說，支那官方公布的數據很少，他知道的資料不會比一般人多，由於臨床數據少，如果香港出現確診個案，只能參考類似的疾病處方藥物，例如沙士、中東呼吸綜合症等；最差的情況是病毒一傳入香港，就已經有數十人感染，出現「超級傳播」的情況，提醒市民不要以為17年前的沙士慘痛教訓歷史一定不會重現。"},{"pid":"ae7eb244e2975635d62c1e41fa6ffed276b9b581","tid":1832188,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"根本就係想重現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8fda7bb5e74ca9919acb879b59fe7e75cafc89","tid":1832188,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:56:00.000Z","msg":"等我仲特登入條LINK睇係咪真係咁堅寫支那,<br />\n原來寫內地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98093cee50ed593e372cec835d8e6159470a9586","tid":1832188,"uid"